data.description: Incredible opportunity to own this beautiful newly built home in highly sought after community in the heart of the recent growth in Menifee.  Backing to a school, instead of busy roads, other homes or still developing ground, this home has one of the best locations in the community!  Upgraded flooring, lighting and fixtures, along with solar for power will save you money!  Enter through covered front porch to the entryway and staircase.   Main floor great room features a huge family room, wide open to the dining area and upgraded kitchen with granite, stainless appliances, center island, walk in pantry and loaded with counter space and storage.  High ceilings and lots of windows keep this home airy and light.  Second floor boasts laundry with linen space, and 3 large bedrooms and 2 baths, including spacious master suite with private bath and walk in closet.  Private back yard is a blank slate, to be finished in whatever way you think best!  Located close to schools, parks, and all the new development with shopping, restaurants and more.  Easy freeway access for commuters make this a dream come true.
